AB- THE STUDY AIMED TO EVALUATE THE DIGITALIZATION, BUSINESS INNOVATION AND COMPANY PERFORMANCE OF MANUFACTURING INDUSTRY IN CHINA AND DEVELOPED AN INNOVATIVE BUSINESS OPERATION FRAMEWORK FOR MANUFACTURING COMPANIES. DESCRIPTIVE DESIGN WAS USED IN THE STUDY TO PROVIDE A COMPREHENSIVE OVERVIEW OF A TOPIC BY COLLECTING DATA FROM A VARIETY OF SOURCES. THIS HELPED TO PROVIDE A MORE COMPLETE PICTURE OF THE TOPIC AND TO IDENTIFY ANY TRENDS OR PATTERNS. SURVEY QUESTIONNAIRE WAS THE TOOL USED IN DATA GATHERING. THE PARTICIPANTS OF THIS STUDY WERE 328 EMPLOYEES FROM TEN MANUFACTURING COMPANIES IN GUANGDONG AND GUANGXI REGIONS IN CHINA.|
